# Session [16] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Default Gateway chist?  
- Tarze kar Default Gateway  
- Estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – Default Gateway Basics
- Default Gateway = device (aksaran router) ke **traffic ra be network digar ersal mikonad**  
- Har device IP address khodesh + subnet mask dare, va traffic be girefte shode baraye network digar → be Default Gateway mirevad  

## Explanation

### Tarze Kar
- default gateway manzor ine darvaze vorod be shabake ya khoroje
- Agar device bekhahad be IP address ke dar LAN nist dastresi peyda konad → packet ra be Default Gateway mifrestad  
- Routers Default Gateway ra check mikonand va packet ra be network motelegh migzarand  

### Estefadeh-ha
- Access be internet  
- Ersal packet be LAN haye digar  
- Simplify routing dar small networks  

### Example
| Device IP | Subnet Mask | Default Gateway |
|-----------|------------|----------------|
| 192.168.1.10 | 255.255.255.0 | 192.168.1.1 |
| 10.0.5.20   | 255.0.0.0     | 10.0.0.1    |

